        <h2 class="title has-text-centered">General information</h2>
        <div class="columns is-centered is-mobile">
            <div class="column is-8-desktop is-8-tablet is-10-mobile">
                <div class="columns">
                    <div class="column">
                        <p>We have 3 training sessions. These are all hosted in deep water at the Olympia leisure centre:</p>
                        <div class="content">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Rookie</strong> 7-8pm Monday
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Juniors</strong> 8-9.30pm Tuesday
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong>Seniors</strong> 8-9.30pm Monday
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    Additionally we have swim session for players every Monday 6-8pm.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column">
                        <div class="image">
                            <img src="/img/water-polo/Olympia-Leisure.jpg" alt="Olympia" class="smooth-corners"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="subtitle has-text-centered">Events</h3>
                <p>We enter a wide variety of competitions every year, including:</p>
                <div class="content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Scottish National League
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            U16 boys, U16 girls, U19 Boys, U19 Girls, Men and Ladies
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>




            </div>
        </div>


    </section>
